            <title>[KAFKA-1578] Controller should de-register all listeners upon designation</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/KAFKA-1578</link>
                <project id="12311720" key="KAFKA">Kafka</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Today in KafkaController.onControllerResignation all the admin path listeners are not de-registered. This will cause multiple controllers listening on the same admin paths, and the fake controllers, upon failing to finish the admin commands, will also delete the admin zk path incorrectly.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
